Command format:

testify [GLOBAL-OPTIONS] [verb [LOCAL-OPTIONS] [noun] [arguments]]

GLOBAL-OPTIONS:
  -C configfile (D=./.testify/config merged on top of ~/.testify/config)
  -d workdir (D=.)

verb:
  add/create
  compare
  config (patterned after git's)
  exit
  help
  init
  list
  modify
  quit
  remove/delete
  run
  show
  update

noun:
  benchmark
  filter
  test
